<trans-unit id="tool.bucket.description">
  <source>Simple tool for filling large closed areas with a specific color.
Use the left mouse button to fill, and the right mouse button to erase.</source>
</trans-unit>
<trans-unit id="tool.erase.description">
  <source>Simple tool for erasing.
Use either the left or right mouse button to erase.</source>
</trans-unit>
<trans-unit id="tool.move.description">
  <source>Allows you to rotate and move your skin without accidentally drawing on it.</source>
</trans-unit>
<trans-unit id="tool.brush.description">
  <source>Simple tool for drawing.
Use the left mouse button to draw, and the right mouse button to erase.</source>
</trans-unit>
<trans-unit id="tool.sculpt.description">
  <source>Copy pixels from base layer to overlay.
Only works when overlay is visible.
Use the left mouse copy pixels up, and the right mouse button to copy them down.</source>
</trans-unit>
<trans-unit id="tool.shade.description">
  <source>Makes pixels lighter/darker or adjusts their color based on the palette.
Use the left mouse button to darken, and the right mouse button to lighten.</source>
</trans-unit>
<trans-unit id="popup_warning.layer.layer_hidden">
  <source>Current layer is not editable (hidden).</source>
</trans-unit>
<trans-unit id="popup_warning.sculpt.overlay_hidden">
  <source>Cannot sculpt without overlay being visible.</source>
</trans-unit>
<trans-unit id="s29c44cbd060628e2">
  <source>Load new Project?
This will replace your current project, and you will lose your history.
Make sure you have saved the current project.</source>
</trans-unit>
<trans-unit id="warning.layer.layer_hidden">
  <source>Current layer is hidden, and cannot be edited.</source>
</trans-unit>
<trans-unit id="warning.layer.filters">
  <source>Colors drawn on the current layer will appear altered by filters.</source>
</trans-unit>
<trans-unit id="warning.blend.blend_enabled">
  <source>Blend palette enabled. Colors drawn might not match color picker.</source>
</trans-unit>
